did.head: OVERVIEW
did.abstract: Marriage certificates (1853-1996) and index (1853-1989), birth certificates (1866-1902) and index (ca. 1870-1931), and death certificates (1870-1909) and index (1890-1931).
did.physloc: See Detailed Description for shelf locations.

scopecontent.p: Alphabetical listing by male and female surnames, along with corresponding marriage certificate volume and page number.
Numerical listing of marriage certificates; on rolls with more than one volume, the volumes may appear in reverse numerical order.
At the beginning of each letter of the alphabet, supplemental births for the years 1876, 1878, and 1881 are listed.
